per-resolution, demonstrate that VRT outperforms the state-of-the-art methods\nby large margins ($\\textbf{up to 2.16dB}$) on fourteen benchmark datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Jan 2022 17:54:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 17:17:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-16"}
