to coupled\nsystems, and also construct several non-constant steady states and analyze\ntheir stability. Finally, numerical simulations are performed to illustrate the\ntheoretical results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Jan 2022 21:19:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 20 Feb 2022 06:40:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-22"}
