rrors in the luminosity distance\nmeasurements and sky localization are mostly in the range of $0.05-0.2$ and\n$1-100\\deg^2$, respectively, for these sBBHs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 29 Jan 2022 06:53:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-01"}
